|BCBThe Barbarians are an offshoot of modern human society that settled south
of Darkwind City in a settlement known as Canith. Their rugged lifestyle
tends towards the development of stronger, healthier bodies than most humans.
Canith society values order, and pursuit of the common good. Barbarians
are generally friendly to strangers and always eager to learn about exotic
people and places.

